---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Results — Jodie Plant Marketing"
  description="Real credentials, proven methodology, and honest results. No fake case studies — here's what I actually bring to the table."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight">
          What You Can Expect
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          I don't have a portfolio of logos to hide behind. Here's what I bring instead — real experience, a proven approach, and the results to back it up.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CREDENTIALS & NUMBERS -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy">The Numbers</h2>

      <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="font-mono text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-navy" data-stat>15+</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Years Experience</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="font-mono text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-navy" data-stat>200+</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Campaigns Delivered</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="font-mono text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-navy" data-stat>$5M+</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Ad Spend Managed</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="font-mono text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-navy" data-stat>95%</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Client Retention</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Outcome Range Anchors -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">What I've Seen Across Engagements</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
            <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-orange">30–120%</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text font-medium">Increase in demo bookings within 90 days</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
            <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-orange">18–40%</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text font-medium">Reduction in cost per lead</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
            <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-orange">2x</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text font-medium">Organic visibility doubled in 6–12 months</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-muted italic">Typical outcome ranges based on historical engagements. Individual results depend on starting position, market, and budget.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE APPROACH IN ACTION -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-light">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy">The Approach in Action</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted max-w-2xl">Instead of fake case studies, here's how I actually work — so you know exactly what you're getting.</p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-10">
        <!-- SEO Engagement -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">What a Typical SEO Engagement Looks Like</h3>
          <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div>
              <p class="font-mono text-sm text-orange font-semibold">Month 1</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Technical audit, keyword research, competitor analysis, AI citation check. Fix critical technical issues.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-mono text-sm text-orange font-semibold">Month 2–3</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Content creation targeting highest-opportunity keywords. On-page optimization. Link outreach begins.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-mono text-sm text-orange font-semibold">Month 4–6</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Content velocity increases. Rankings start moving. AI citations begin appearing. First leads from organic.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-mono text-sm text-orange font-semibold">Month 6–12</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Compounding results. Consistent lead flow from search. Expand to new keyword clusters. Ongoing optimization.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Startup Launch -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">How I'd Approach a Startup Launch Campaign</h3>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-xs text-orange font-bold">1</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted"><span class="text-text font-medium">Positioning &amp; messaging:</span> Nail the value proposition. Who you serve, what you do differently, why they should care.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-xs text-orange font-bold">2</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted"><span class="text-text font-medium">Channel prioritization:</span> Based on your audience, budget, and timeline — which channels will move the needle fastest?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-xs text-orange font-bold">3</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted"><span class="text-text font-medium">Launch execution:</span> Landing pages, ad campaigns, content, email sequences — coordinated to create momentum.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-xs text-orange font-bold">4</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted"><span class="text-text font-medium">Learn &amp; iterate:</span> First 30 days generate data. Optimize based on real signals, not assumptions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Monthly Retainer -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">What a Monthly Retainer Delivers</h3>
          <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy text-sm">Strategy &amp; Planning</h4>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted">
                <li>• Monthly strategy call</li>
                <li>• Performance review &amp; action plan</li>
                <li>• Competitive monitoring report</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy text-sm">Content &amp; SEO</h4>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted">
                <li>• Blog posts / thought leadership pieces</li>
                <li>• On-page SEO optimization</li>
                <li>• AI citation monitoring</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy text-sm">Paid &amp; Social</h4>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted">
                <li>• Campaign management &amp; optimization</li>
                <li>• Creative refreshes</li>
                <li>• Social media scheduling</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy text-sm">Reporting</h4>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted">
                <li>• Monthly performance dashboard</li>
                <li>• ROI tracking &amp; attribution</li>
                <li>• Next-month recommendations</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PEEK UNDER THE HOOD -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy">Peek Under the Hood</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted max-w-2xl">AI-enhanced workflows aren't just a buzzword. Here's what the actual process looks like.</p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-navy/5 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center border border-gray-200">
            <div class="text-center px-6">
              <p class="font-mono text-sm text-orange font-semibold">AI Visibility Report</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted">Search position analysis &middot; AI citation check &middot; Competitor gaps &middot; Priority actions</p>
              <div class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-left max-w-xs mx-auto">
                <div class="h-3 bg-orange/20 rounded w-full"></div>
                <div class="h-3 bg-navy/10 rounded w-4/5"></div>
                <div class="h-3 bg-navy/10 rounded w-3/5"></div>
                <div class="h-3 bg-orange/20 rounded w-4/5"></div>
                <div class="h-3 bg-navy/10 rounded w-2/3"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">Sample visibility report structure — every engagement starts with a clear picture of where you stand.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-navy/5 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center border border-gray-200">
            <div class="text-center px-6">
              <p class="font-mono text-sm text-orange font-semibold">Monthly Dashboard</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted">Traffic &middot; Conversions &middot; Rankings &middot; ROI</p>
              <div class="mt-4 flex gap-4 justify-center">
                <div class="w-16">
                  <div class="h-20 bg-orange/30 rounded-t"></div>
                  <div class="h-12 bg-orange/20 rounded-b"></div>
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-muted mt-1">Organic</p>
                </div>
                <div class="w-16">
                  <div class="h-14 bg-indigo/30 rounded-t"></div>
                  <div class="h-18 bg-indigo/20 rounded-b"></div>
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-muted mt-1">Paid</p>
                </div>
                <div class="w-16">
                  <div class="h-24 bg-navy/20 rounded-t"></div>
                  <div class="h-8 bg-navy/10 rounded-b"></div>
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-muted mt-1">Direct</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">Reporting you can actually understand — not 50-page decks that gather dust.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT CLIENTS SAY -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-light">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy">What People Say</h2>

      <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <blockquote class="text-text leading-relaxed italic">
            "Jodie doesn't just execute — she thinks strategically about the whole picture. The kind of marketer who makes you feel like you have a CMO on your team."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy text-sm">— Testimonial placeholder</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted">Real testimonials and LinkedIn recommendations will be added here</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <blockquote class="text-text leading-relaxed italic">
            "What sets Jodie apart is the combination of deep expertise and the willingness to actually do the work. No handoffs to juniors, no shortcuts."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy text-sm">— Testimonial placeholder</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted">Real testimonials and LinkedIn recommendations will be added here</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INDUSTRIES -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy">Industries &amp; Experience</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted max-w-2xl">I work with tech companies. I understand your buyers, your sales cycles, and your competitive landscape.</p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4">
        {['SaaS', 'Fintech', 'Dev Tools', 'AI / ML', 'MarTech', 'B2B Tech'].map(industry => (
          <div class="bg-light rounded-lg p-4 text-center border border-gray-100">
            <p class="font-medium text-navy text-sm">{industry}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <p class="mt-8 text-muted">
        I've seen what works for companies like yours. Pattern recognition across hundreds of campaigns means faster time-to-results and fewer expensive mistakes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-navy text-white">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold">Want to see what I'd do for your company?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-white/70 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Start with a free visibility snapshot — I'll show you exactly where you stand and what to do about it.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-orange text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-lg hover:bg-orange/90 transition-colors min-h-[44px]">
          Get Your Free Visibility Snapshot
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
